Distant Worlds Universe REFRESHED (DWUR)

https://github.com/salemonz/DWUR

Full forum post: https://www.matrixgames.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=10492&t=395506

/========== About ==========\
For years I have enjoyed Distant Worlds Universe. This mod compilation is my attempt to give back to the community by combining the best DWU gameplay and visual enhancements into one experience. It features completely redesigned aliens (all 45 races from Haree78's Extended Mod...whew!), all new shipsets, new planet graphics, new/refreshed sounds, new/refreshed UI elements and an integrated variety of the best DWU gameplay mods out there (IMO).
-- Salemonz

v1.5.0 -- 24 March 2026 -- New engine exhaust graphics. New ground-unit icons. New race pics (group shots). Component balance pass incorporated. 14 game files edited. Weapons/fighters changed. Tech research orders altered for 10 races. Refreshed all 194 components. New images (many pulled from my DW2 mods). Refreshed flags. 75 new empire flags. 75 new pirate flags. Balance pass incorporated. 2K files edited/changed. Race stats, AI policies, design templates, pirate behavior...even dialog during diplomacy have all been refreshed. 46 races in DWUR should all behave and play very differently. Updated pirate portraits.

v1.2.0 -- 04 March 2026 -- Updated portraits for 25 races. Updated alert sound due to user request. Updated hyperdeny graphic for better visibility. Updated UI character icons for better visibility. Renamed/changed several races to help them fit in with the overall spread.
